xdg-user-dirs-gtk
------------------------------------------
xdg-user-dirs-gtk is a companion to xdg-user-dirs that integrates it 
into the Gnome desktop and Gtk+ applications.

It gets run during login and does two things:
* Tracks changes of locale and prompts the user so the directories
  can be changed.
* Creates a default gtk bookmarks file if there is none, based
  on a set of xdg user dirs.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  glib2-2.12.9-1
  gtk2-x11-2.10.9-1
  libintl8-0.15-1
  xdg-user-dirs-0.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  autoconf2.5-2.61-1
  automake1.9-1.9.6-2
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.2.11-1
  gawk-3.1.5-4
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  intltool-0.35.4-1
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.21-1
  sed-4.1.5-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.gnome.org/

Canonical download:
  ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/gnome/sources/xdg-user-dirs-gtk/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /etc/xdg/autostart/user-dirs-update-gtk.desktop
  /usr/bin/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-update.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4.README
  /usr/share/doc/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4/ABOUT-NLS
  /usr/share/doc/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/xdg-user-dirs-gtk-0.4/README
  /usr/share/locale/de/LC_MESSAGES/xdg-user-dirs-gtk.mo
  /usr/share/locale/ja/LC_MESSAGES/xdg-user-dirs-gtk.mo
  /usr/share/locale/nb/LC_MESSAGES/xdg-user-dirs-gtk.mo
  /usr/share/locale/nn/LC_MESSAGES/xdg-user-dirs-gtk.mo

